	<h2>About me</h2>
	<p>Although I'm a designer at heart, you can often find me building bridges across the murky waters of marketing, branding,
		art, and building resources for fellow creatives.</p>
	<p>I've previously worked with B2B, B2C, and public-sector teams from <a href="https://www.gre.ac.uk/las/design" target="_blank"
