			rel="noopener noreferrer">Blueberry</a>. In this lifetime, I've also dipped my toes in <a
			href="/playground/">other creative disciplines</a>, including music production, exhibition curation, visual art, social media content, and photography.
	<p>I now partner with people who care deeply about what they do, and I help them solve problems with their website, mailing list, SEO, or marketing operations. My superpower? I'm no specialist. The beauty of not being stuck in one corner is that, unlike specialists, 1) I don't wear blinders, 2) I can see the big picture, and 3) I can get you out of (almost) any quandary.</p>
